<Game>
	<Name>Derby Stallion II (Japan)</Name>
	<plot>Overview:Derby Stallion II is a 1994 horse raising and racing simulation game from ASCII Corporation and the sequel to 1991's Best Keiba Derby Stallion. While the original Derby Stallion saw a few enhanced versions, such as Derby Stallion: Zengokuban or Derby Stallion: DOS/V Edition, Derby Stallion II is the first proper sequel.The goal of the game is to raise a stable of racehorses and make a fortune racing and breeding them.	</plot>
